  <brief_title>Mitral Valve Area Assessment: Comparison With Transthoracic Echocardiography and Magnetic Resonance Imaging</brief_title>
  <official_title>Quantification of Rheumatic Mitral Stenosis With Cardiac Magnetic Resonance Imaging and Comparison With Transthoracic Echocardiography</official_title>
